<li>In cricket, the <a href="/wiki/Mumbai_Indians" title="Mumbai Indians">Mumbai Indians</a> win the <a href="/wiki/2017_Indian_Premier_League" title="2017 Indian Premier League">Indian Premier League</a>, defeating the <a href="/wiki/Rising_Pune_Supergiant" title="Rising Pune Supergiant">Rising Pune Supergiant</a> in <b><a href="/wiki/2017_Indian_Premier_League_Final" title="2017 Indian Premier League Final">the final</a></b>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Hassan_Rouhani" title="Hassan Rouhani">Hassan Rouhani</a> is <b><a href="/wiki/Iranian_presidential_election,_2017" title="Iranian presidential election, 2017">re-elected</a></b> <a href="/wiki/President_of_Iran" title="President of Iran">President of Iran</a>.</li>
